Andile Mpisane and his wife Tamia welcomed their newborn daughter on Sunday. Andile is now a father to three daughters, two whom he has with his ex-lover Sithelo Shozi. The exciting news was shared by his mother Shauwn Mkhize, who was beaming with excitement as she welcomed another granddaughter. Taking to social media Shauwn mentioned that the little girl is named Miaandy. She also stated that Tamia was recovering well in hospital and Andile was tired but also in good spirits. “The Mpisane, Louw, and Mkhize family are pleased to announce the arrival of Baby Miaandy,” she wrote.  Also Read: Inside Tamia Mpisane’s stunning baby shower For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.